        meta: "2 reviews | 0 photos",
        date: "6 Mar 2025",
        rating: 5,
        quote: "We recently had the pleasure of working with KB to secure our home loan for our dream house, and we can't speak highly enough of his outstanding service!.\n\nKB went above and beyond to ensure that our loan application process was seamless and stress-free. His super-friendly demeanor, prompt communication (even on holidays!), and flexibility to meet at a time and location that suited us were truly impressive.\n\nKB's expertise and knowledge of the loan process were evident throughout our interactions. He took the time to explain everything clearly, addressed all our concerns, and made sure we understood each step of the way.",
